outfit_data.top: A crisp white silk blouse with a ruffled neckline and three-quarter sleeves. The fabric drapes beautifully and has a subtle sheen for a touch of elegance.
outfit_data.bottom: Navy blue wool cigarette pants with a slightly flared leg, tailored to flatter the feminine silhouette. They offer both style and comfort for an evening at the beach.
outfit_data.shoes: Black patent leather pointed-toe heels with a comfortable mid-height.  The classic style adds a touch of sophistication without being too formal.
outfit_data.extras: A beige wool trench coat cinched at the waist with a brown leather belt to ward off any cool breezes and add a vintage charm.
